Class Garden

java.lang.Object
  Garden

public class Garden
extends java.lang.Object

The Garden class is a 2D array of Patches. It sets up all of the Patches with their neighbors, runs each patch, and can print out an image of the the 2D Patch array, showing where there are Plants and where not.
